ScalaMiniTwitter
-----------------

Hi There,

Welcome to my Mini Twitter.

The mini twitter contains 3 Scala Actors - Alice, Bob and Charlie.

The 3 Musketeers or actors can follow or subscribe to each other.
They can post messages or tweets on to their mailbox.
They can also view messages send to their mailbox i.e they can view their respective walls.

These are some sample commands to input when prompted by this application.(myTwitter.scala)
Sample Inputs
-------------
posting:Alice->Halo there
following:Alice follows Bob
following:Alice follows Charlie
posting:Bob->Hi Alice
posting:Charlie->Hi All
wall:Alice wall

Output
-------
Charlie - Hi All (2 seconds ago)
Bob - Hi Alice (4 seconds ago)
Alice - Halo there (2 minutes ago)
